snippet.title: FUMEHEAD - Trailer | Turn-based and worm-hunting story RPG
snippet.description:
FUMEHEAD is a hero-focused turn-based RPG set in a post-abandonment underground world. Play as Jack & Ami as you try to eradicate the new alien disease that calls itself Slither.

Wishlist on steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3194740/FUMEHEAD/
Join Discord:  https://discord.gg/kwtVDh8BXp
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/FUMEHEAD/
X: https://x.com/fume_head
